<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 14:09:42 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列军队关闭加沙边境附近的大片高速公路以迎接大规模祈祷</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-12/ty-article/.premium/idf-closes-swath-of-highways-near-gaza-border-in-lead-up-to-mass-prayer/00000191-464b-dbfd-a7f3-7f6ff2dc0000</link><description>这次集会是由右翼团体在犹太斋戒日 Tisha B&amp;#39;Av 之前组织的，预计将吸引数百人，其中包括议会成员。组织者将其描述为“朝着目标——在整个加沙地带建立犹太人定居点”迈出的一步。</description><pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 11:50:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-12/ty-article/.premium/idf-closes-swath-of-highways-near-gaza-border-in-lead-up-to-mass-prayer/00000191-464b-dbfd-a7f3-7f6ff2dc0000</guid></item><item><title>消息来源：哈马斯拒绝新提议并不意味着与以色列的谈判破裂</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-12/ty-article/.premium/sources-hamas-rejection-of-new-proposals-doesnt-indicate-collapse-of-talks-with-israel/00000191-4601-dcc2-a9d1-4ed94e380000</link><description>哈马斯呼吁调解人提出一项计划，从四月份开始实施拜登大纲，而不是提出任何关于人质/停火协议的新提议，这主要被视为一种战术举措，旨在在与以色列恢复谈判之前施加压力。至来源</description><pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 10:37:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-12/ty-article/.premium/sources-hamas-rejection-of-new-proposals-doesnt-indicate-collapse-of-talks-with-israel/00000191-4601-dcc2-a9d1-4ed94e380000</guid></item><item><title>值得吗？关于以色列袭击中东的十大紧迫问题</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-08-12/ty-article-opinion/.premium/was-it-worth-it-ten-burning-questions-about-israels-attacks-in-the-middle-east/00000191-45d8-d49b-a7f7-6ddc78730000</link><description></description><pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 09:43:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-08-12/ty-article-opinion/.premium/was-it-worth-it-ten-burning-questions-about-israels-attacks-in-the-middle-east/00000191-45d8-d49b-a7f7-6ddc78730000</guid></item><item><title>在最初的失败之后，以色列军队正在研究挽救极端正统派男子征召动力的方法</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-12/ty-article/.premium/after-initial-failures-idf-examines-ways-to-salvage-drive-to-draft-ultra-orthodox-men/00000191-45cc-debc-a793-4dec2e040000</link><description>以色列国防军人力局正在考虑让极端正统派男子到其常规入伍中心以外的地点报到，以减少他们遇到示威者的机会，并将征召日期延长一段时间</description><pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 09:16:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-12/ty-article/.premium/after-initial-failures-idf-examines-ways-to-salvage-drive-to-draft-ultra-orthodox-men/00000191-45cc-debc-a793-4dec2e040000</guid></item><item><title>前以色列国防军将军转为政治家的亚伊尔·戈兰：“不确定”以色列是否是一个民主国家</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-12/ty-article/former-idf-deputy-chief-says-he-is-not-sure-israel-is-a-democracy-anymore/00000191-457b-dcc2-a9d1-4ffb78d50000</link><description>以色列新成立的中左翼政党民主党党魁亚伊尔·戈兰在接受《卫报》采访时表示支持两国解决方案，但强调这一过程可能需要数年时间。 “现在，我们是一个饱受创伤的国家。人们失去了安全感”</description><pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 07:53:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-12/ty-article/former-idf-deputy-chief-says-he-is-not-sure-israel-is-a-democracy-anymore/00000191-457b-dcc2-a9d1-4ffb78d50000</guid></item><item><title>以色列士兵在加沙地带战斗中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-12/ty-article/israeli-soldier-killed-in-gaza-strip-fighting/00000191-44f7-d621-a3db-d6f7137f0000</link><description>以色列国防军确认这名士兵是 19 岁的中士。 Omer Ginzburg，一名来自以色列北部的 19 岁伞兵</description><pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 05:14:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-12/ty-article/israeli-soldier-killed-in-gaza-strip-fighting/00000191-44f7-d621-a3db-d6f7137f0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡在嘲笑总理的“全面胜利”后指责加兰特的“反以色列”议程</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-12/ty-article-live/idf-releases-name-of-combat-soldier-killed-in-southern-gaza-fighting/00000191-4452-d122-a7f5-ff77ca190000</link><description>伊朗代理外长表示，德黑兰有权对以色列采取适当和威慑性的反应 ■ 英国、法国和德国领导人敦促伊朗不要破坏停火、人质谈判 ■ 以色列军队称向纳哈里亚地区发射了 30 枚火箭弹，真主党声称对此负责 ■ 以色列国防军一名士兵在加沙南部丧生 ■ 美国宣布潜艇移至中东</description><pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 03:13:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-12/ty-article-live/idf-releases-name-of-combat-soldier-killed-in-southern-gaza-fighting/00000191-4452-d122-a7f5-ff77ca190000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡政府在战争中推进司法政变，几乎没有反对</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-12/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-government-plows-ahead-with-judicial-coup-amid-war-and-with-little-opposition/00000191-42d7-dcc2-a9d1-4edf74230000</link><description>在基本不感兴趣的媒体、缺乏灵感的反对派和厌倦战争的公众的眼皮底下，内塔尼亚胡和他的走狗正忙着通过诋毁以色列的看门人来迎合他们的支持者</description><pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 02:56:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-12/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-government-plows-ahead-with-judicial-coup-amid-war-and-with-little-opposition/00000191-42d7-dcc2-a9d1-4edf74230000</guid></item><item><title>以色列内阁秘书告诉AG：你们的工作程序有缺陷，而不是内塔尼亚胡的</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-11/ty-article/.premium/israels-cabinet-secretary-tells-ag-your-work-procedures-are-flawed-not-netanyahus/00000191-42e8-d8bb-a5df-fff9178a0000</link><description>以色列总检察长告诉内塔尼亚胡，他的内阁工作程序存在缺陷，损害了公共利益——对国家安全造成严重影响——之后，内阁秘书指控总检察长超越了她的职权</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Aug 2024 20:05:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-11/ty-article/.premium/israels-cabinet-secretary-tells-ag-your-work-procedures-are-flawed-not-netanyahus/00000191-42e8-d8bb-a5df-fff9178a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列司法部长敦促政府恢复司法改革</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-11/ty-article/.premium/israels-justice-minister-urges-government-to-resume-judicial-overhaul/00000191-4262-dcbf-a3bb-e7ff61820000</link><description>在几位联盟议员呼吁罢免总检察长后，以色列司法部长亚里夫·莱文敦促他们与他一起努力重启司法改革，特别是通过一项法律，让政府对法官的选择有更多的控制权</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Aug 2024 17:51:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-11/ty-article/.premium/israels-justice-minister-urges-government-to-resume-judicial-overhaul/00000191-4262-dcbf-a3bb-e7ff61820000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡还是人质？美国犹太人是时候做出选择了</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-08-11/ty-article/.highlight/netanyahu-or-the-hostages-its-time-for-u-s-jews-to-choose/00000191-4207-debc-a793-4eaf49200000</link><description>每个关心以色列和人质的人都必须做出决定，他们是与被哈马斯扣押的人质家属站在一起，还是与失败的政客站在一起，我们永远不应该忘记，在这场暴行发生时，他们仍在掌权。</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Aug 2024 17:22:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-08-11/ty-article/.highlight/netanyahu-or-the-hostages-its-time-for-u-s-jews-to-choose/00000191-4207-debc-a793-4eaf49200000</guid></item><item><title>以色列在约旦河西岸驾车枪击事件中丧生，一人受伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-11/ty-article/.premium/israeli-killed-one-wounded-in-drive-by-shooting-attack-in-west-bank/00000191-41fa-d8bb-a5df-fffbcc3e0000</link><description>以色列军方认为，袭击者在西岸北部的90号公路上向一辆车开枪，随后继续行驶，并向第二辆车开枪。救援部门宣布一名受害者当场死亡</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Aug 2024 17:08:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-11/ty-article/.premium/israeli-killed-one-wounded-in-drive-by-shooting-attack-in-west-bank/00000191-41fa-d8bb-a5df-fffbcc3e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列处于战争状态，第 310 天：据报道，官员要求真主党推迟对以色列袭击的答复</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-11/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-310-officials-reportedly-ask-hezbollah-to-delay-reply-to-israel-strike/00000191-4234-d8bb-a5df-ffb520160000</link><description>以色列消息人士告诉《国土报》，以色列有迹象表明哈马斯领导人辛瓦尔希望达成停火/释放人质协议，并补充说“问题是内塔尼亚胡是否愿意” ■ 以色列男子在约旦河西岸枪击事件中丧生 ■ 以色列政府采纳阻止协议访问真主党附属新闻频道 Al-Mayadeen ■ 这是战争 310 天后您需要了解的内容</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Aug 2024 16:24:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-11/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-310-officials-reportedly-ask-hezbollah-to-delay-reply-to-israel-strike/00000191-4234-d8bb-a5df-ffb520160000</guid></item><item><title>如果加沙人质谈判失败，美国和其他调解人威胁称以色列和哈马斯将出面</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-11/ty-article/.premium/u-s-and-other-mediators-threaten-to-call-out-israel-hamas-if-gaza-hostage-talks-fail/00000191-415c-d283-ad9f-e1fe88090000</link><description>一位外交消息人士告诉《国土报》，拜登政府——迄今为止一直将谈判陷入僵局归咎于哈马斯——已经到了这样的地步：内塔尼亚胡总理的行为将导致美国公开指责他破坏谈判并阻止人质获释。</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Aug 2024 16:20:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-11/ty-article/.premium/u-s-and-other-mediators-threaten-to-call-out-israel-hamas-if-gaza-hostage-talks-fail/00000191-415c-d283-ad9f-e1fe88090000</guid></item><item><title>新研究揭示了加沙地带被释放的以色列母亲和儿童的精神和身体创伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-11/ty-article/.premium/new-study-reveals-mental-physical-traumas-of-israelis-freed-from-captivity-in-gaza/00000191-41fc-d8bb-a5df-fffdbc420000</link><description>这项新研究以 11 月与哈马斯达成人质协议后返回以色列的 19 名青年和 7 名妇女为基础，揭示了在加沙被囚禁 50 天的影响，以及大多数人目睹谋杀或绑架的最初袭击家庭成员的</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Aug 2024 16:14:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-11/ty-article/.premium/new-study-reveals-mental-physical-traumas-of-israelis-freed-from-captivity-in-gaza/00000191-41fc-d8bb-a5df-fffdbc420000</guid></item><item><title>以色列以国家安全为由封锁真主党附属新闻频道 Al Mayadeen</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-11/ty-article/israel-blocks-hezbollah-affiliated-news-channel-al-mayadeen-citing-national-security/00000191-41da-d2c9-af99-67fb323c0000</link><description>这项立法由议会于 4 月 1 日通过，政府于 5 月一致通过，授权通讯部长下令外国频道停止广播 45 天。</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Aug 2024 15:29:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-11/ty-article/israel-blocks-hezbollah-affiliated-news-channel-al-mayadeen-citing-national-security/00000191-41da-d2c9-af99-67fb323c0000</guid></item><item><title>右翼抗议者袭击以色列国防军高级律师的家，抗议巴勒斯坦被拘留者的虐待行为</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-11/ty-article/.premium/right-wingers-descend-on-top-idf-lawyers-home-over-probe-of-palestinian-detainees-abuse/00000191-419b-d2c9-af99-67bbf62d0000</link><description>以色列军事倡导者伊法特·托梅尔·耶鲁沙尔米 (Yifat Tomer-Yerushalmi) 将军在长期阴谋论中成为右翼最新的恶魔，该阴谋论声称左翼正在利用司法越权来控制国家，目前她正在起诉涉嫌虐待巴勒斯坦被拘留者的以色列国防军士兵。斯德泰曼拘留中心</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Aug 2024 15:22:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-11/ty-article/.premium/right-wingers-descend-on-top-idf-lawyers-home-over-probe-of-palestinian-detainees-abuse/00000191-419b-d2c9-af99-67bbf62d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军法院将五名涉嫌虐待斯德泰曼巴勒斯坦被拘留者的士兵的逮捕期限延长三天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-11/ty-article/.premium/idf-prosecution-extends-arrest-of-5-soldiers-suspected-of-abusing-palestinian-detainee/00000191-41d7-dcbf-a3bb-e5dfda400000</link><description>军事法庭法官裁定将以色列国防军预备役人员的逮捕期限延长三天，称收集到的证据否定了他们辩护小组提供的医学解释。检方表示，不反对在可能将嫌疑人软禁之前对他们的拘留进行审查</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Aug 2024 15:19:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-11/ty-article/.premium/idf-prosecution-extends-arrest-of-5-soldiers-suspected-of-abusing-palestinian-detainee/00000191-41d7-dcbf-a3bb-e5dfda400000</guid></item><item><title>AG：以色列无法资助为以色列国防军服役的极端正统派男子的孩子提供日托服务</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-11/ty-article/.premium/ag-israel-cannot-finance-daycare-for-ultra-orthodox-slated-for-idf-service/00000191-4190-d505-a39b-d9b42d830000</link><description>据以色列总检察长称，由于高等法院裁定不准极端正统派男子服兵役，因此国家不能再为因应征加入以色列国防军的犹太学院学生的孩子提供日托费用</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Aug 2024 15:11:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-11/ty-article/.premium/ag-israel-cannot-finance-daycare-for-ultra-orthodox-slated-for-idf-service/00000191-4190-d505-a39b-d9b42d830000</guid></item><item><title>以色列节目报道了被绑架到加沙的被释放的人质兄弟姐妹，以争夺艾美奖</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-11/ty-article/.premium/israeli-show-up-for-emmy-for-covering-freed-hostage-siblings-kidnapped-into-gaza/00000191-41a6-d2c9-af99-67a79a7c0000</link><description>以色列调查新闻电视节目《Uvda》因题为“被囚禁的兄弟姐妹”的片段获得提名，该片段对获释人质 Itay 和 Maya Regev 进行了深入采访，他们参加了 Nova 节日，并于 10 月 7 日被哈马斯劫持为人质</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Aug 2024 14:24:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-11/ty-article/.premium/israeli-show-up-for-emmy-for-covering-freed-hostage-siblings-kidnapped-into-gaza/00000191-41a6-d2c9-af99-67a79a7c0000</guid></item></channel></rss>